sentences: Abdulmajid Aliyu (born 1 June 1994) known professionally as Zayn Africa, is a Nigerian singer, songwriter & record producer.
In 2017, he released a musical studio album titled "The Relationship" with 11 tracks which earned him artistic recognition in Nigeria.
Music AlbumIn 2020, Zayn was featured in a Nigerian Hausa Hip-Hop musical song titled "Da so samu ne".
